Change Log
==========

Features (requested)
--------------------
- Add new Manager Trigger 
    - Beanstalk
- Add new Manager Process
    - System (isolates a process)

Version 1.0 (roadmap)
---------------------
+ multiple IPC adapters `(none, filesystem, shared memory, database)
- multiple Manager Process Adapters (same, child, parallel)
- multiple Manager Trigger (interval, cron, gearman)
- Add tools
    - cron restart script (for restarting after critical errors)
    - boot script (/etc/init.d/phptaskdaemon)
- Example Tasks
    - Tutorial (minimal, advanced, gearman)
    - Statistics (gatherStatistics, sendReport, checkExcessiveRuntime)
- Create user documentation
    - Doc directory (INSTALL, USAGE, TUTORIAL)
    - Website/Wiki


Version 0.8.3 (planned)
-----------------------
- Implement daemon status action
    - define (recursive) data structure of ipc segments
    - read multiple ipc adapter types 
- Implement manager triggers
    + Interval
    - Cron
    + Gearman
- Implement daemon monitoring action
- Add tutorial tasks
    + Minimal
    - Gearman


Version 0.8.2 (26-10-2011)
==========================
+ Implement loading task components by config file
+ Implement running a single task
+ Implement IPC adapters
    + DataBase
    + File
    + Shared Memory
+ Add more unit tests


Version 0.8.1 (16-10-2011)
--------------------------
+ Implement Task loader class
+ Implement basic IPC adapters
    + None
+ Implement basic Trigger adapter
    - Same
+ Implement basic Process adapter
    - Interval
+ Implement loading task components by class definition
+ Refactoring
    + Extract task loading methods to seperate class
    + Rename BaseClasses to DefaultClasses 


Version 0.8 (14-10-2011)
